snippet.title: Wheel Of Fortune
snippet.description: Welcome to Wheel of Fortune's official YouTube page. Wheel of Fortune has been the #1 syndicated series since its inception and has earned 7 Daytime Emmy Awards. With more than 27 million viewers per week, syndication's most successful series continues to attract a larger audience than many primetime television shows.
